description: [``botocore``] Updated the CreateIntegrationAssociation API to support the CASES_DOMAIN IntegrationType.

[``botocore``] This release adds APIs for Amazon Connect Cases. Cases allows your agents to quickly track and manage customer issues that require multiple interactions, follow-up tasks, and teams in your contact center.  For more information, see https://docs.aws.amazon.com/cases/latest/APIReference/Welcome.html
[``botocore``] Added EnableNetworkAddressUsageMetrics flag for ModifyVpcAttribute, DescribeVpcAttribute APIs.
[``botocore``] Documentation updates to address various Amazon ECS tickets.
[``botocore``] S3 Object Lambda adds support to allow customers to intercept HeadObject and ListObjects requests and introduce their own compute. These requests were previously proxied to S3.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for impersonation roles in Amazon WorkMail.
